190
00:13:57,750 --> 00:13:58,590
Xiu.

191
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:00,480
Xiu.

192
00:14:05,510 --> 00:14:07,280
Xiu.

193
00:14:07,550 --> 00:14:08,670
